<font color=#FFFF00>"O N O's  I D O L"</font>

01:11.020 --> 01:12.155
Mtoto!

01:12.160 --> 01:13.437
Where'd you go?

01:13.442 --> 01:15.257
Mtoto?

01:15.446 --> 01:17.429
Here I am! (LAUGHS)

01:18.449 --> 01:21.866
Okay, you got us!
(ALL LAUGHING)

01:21.871 --> 01:23.095
Wait.

01:23.100 --> 01:24.765
Do you hear that?

01:24.770 --> 01:26.898
I don't hear anything.

01:28.107 --> 01:29.527
(GASPS)

01:31.512 --> 01:32.945
(SQUAWKING)

01:34.037 --> 01:35.984
Are those birds?

01:35.989 --> 01:37.561
A lot of birds.

01:39.360 --> 01:40.484
(WHIMPERS)

01:40.489 --> 01:43.864
You don't think they're
vultures, do you?

01:43.869 --> 01:45.369
Vultures?

01:47.244 --> 01:48.695
You know who we need right now?

01:48.700 --> 01:50.992
KION: Lion Guard, this way!

01:52.114 --> 01:53.452
Hi, Beshte!

01:53.457 --> 01:54.474
Hey, Mtoto!

01:54.479 --> 01:57.067
That's an un-Bunga-lievable
bunch of birds!

01:57.072 --> 01:59.726
Yeah. I wonder what's going on.

02:03.433 --> 02:05.375
Look at that!

02:06.418 --> 02:09.335
I've never seen so many
birds in one place.

02:09.340 --> 02:11.505
So what are they all doing here?

02:11.510 --> 02:13.411
I bet Ono could tell us.

02:13.416 --> 02:16.419
But I don't know where he is.
ONO: I'm right here!

02:16.424 --> 02:18.233
I got us a spot right in front!

02:18.238 --> 02:20.286
In front of what?

02:20.291 --> 02:21.896
Let's find out.

02:23.347 --> 02:25.240
Can you believe
he's really back?

02:25.245 --> 02:26.424
After all this time?

02:26.429 --> 02:28.239
Who?
Hadithi!

02:28.244 --> 02:29.348
Who-dithi?

02:29.353 --> 02:30.481
Hadithi?

02:30.486 --> 02:32.053
The legendary eagle?

02:32.058 --> 02:34.716
Every bird in the Pride Lands
has heard of him!

02:34.721 --> 02:37.323
Uh, Ono, we aren't birds!

02:37.328 --> 02:40.405
But you don't have to be a
bird to have heard of Hadithi.

02:40.410 --> 02:42.778
Creator of the Hadithi Spin?

02:42.783 --> 02:44.864
Three mid-air loops
and a corkscrew?

02:44.869 --> 02:46.232
I think.

02:46.237 --> 02:49.335
I've always wanted to ask
Hadithi exactly how it goes.

02:49.340 --> 02:50.685
And now I can.

02:50.690 --> 02:52.575
If I can get up
the nerve, that is.

02:52.580 --> 02:54.263
He's kind of my idol.

02:54.268 --> 02:55.645
He sounds <i> Poa,</i> Ono.

02:55.650 --> 02:57.013
Oh, he is.

02:57.018 --> 02:58.403
And smart.

02:58.408 --> 03:00.212
They say whenever he speaks,

03:00.217 --> 03:02.481
nuggets of wisdom 
fall from his mouth.

03:02.486 --> 03:04.481
Pfft! Big deal.

03:04.486 --> 03:06.739
Nuggets fall outta
my mouth all the time.

03:06.744 --> 03:09.324
(BIRDS SQUAWKING AND CHIRPING)

03:12.846 --> 03:15.317
Greetings, my friends.

03:15.322 --> 03:17.719
Say something wise, Hadithi!

03:17.724 --> 03:20.258
The higher you fly,

03:20.337 --> 03:22.818
the more they'll look up to you.

03:22.823 --> 03:25.247
ALL: Ahhhh! Ooooooooooh!

03:25.252 --> 03:28.544
"The higher you fly, the more
they'll look up to you."

03:28.549 --> 03:30.034
That is so deep.

03:30.039 --> 03:32.478
Really? Seems kind of
obvious to me.

03:32.483 --> 03:34.243
Bunga, shh!

03:34.248 --> 03:36.372
Ono really likes this guy!

03:36.377 --> 03:37.731
Isn't he amazing?

03:37.736 --> 03:39.147
Oh, yeah!

03:39.152 --> 03:40.075
Hey, Ono.

03:40.080 --> 03:41.724
Let's ask him about
his spin thingie.

03:41.729 --> 03:43.355
Yo, Hadithi!

03:43.360 --> 03:44.457
Bunga!

03:44.462 --> 03:47.113
You can't just talk to Hadithi.

03:47.118 --> 03:49.550
He's the Raven Rescuer
from Red Rocks.

03:49.555 --> 03:52.152
The Starling Savior
at Summer Springs.

03:52.157 --> 03:55.316
Don't forget the Guardian
of the Great Egret Escape.

03:55.321 --> 03:58.261
Oh, I would never...
(GASPS)

03:58.266 --> 03:59.644
Uh, Bunga?

03:59.649 --> 04:02.097
Is Hadithi
actually talking to me?

04:02.102 --> 04:04.589
Indeed I am, young Egret.

04:04.594 --> 04:06.582
You seem to know a lot about me.

04:06.587 --> 04:09.415
Oh, I do, Hadithi.

04:09.420 --> 04:10.339
Sir.

04:10.344 --> 04:12.094
(CLEARS THROAT) In fact,

04:12.099 --> 04:14.665
I would have to say I'm your

04:14.670 --> 04:15.774
biggest fan?

04:15.779 --> 04:17.144
My biggest fan?

04:17.149 --> 04:19.899
(CHUCKLES) Are you
sure, young Egret?

04:19.904 --> 04:22.238
As you can see, I have many.

04:24.535 --> 04:27.199
<i>♪ I'm not one for boasting</i>

04:27.204 --> 04:29.134
<i>♪ But what they say is true!</i>

04:29.139 --> 04:33.138
<i>♪ I happen to be the best
at everything I do</i>

04:33.143 --> 04:37.276
<i>♪ So what's the point of
fighting the energetic crowd</i>

04:37.281 --> 04:39.411
<i>♪ When they want
to scream and shout</i>

04:39.416 --> 04:43.082
<i>♪ And chant my name out loud</i>

04:43.087 --> 04:44.383
<i>♪ Hadithi, the hero!</i>

04:44.388 --> 04:47.119
<i>♪ Wherever I go</i>

04:47.124 --> 04:48.420
<i>♪ Hadithi, the hero!</i>

04:48.425 --> 04:50.556
<i>♪ They worship me so</i>

04:50.561 --> 04:52.458
<i>♪ Hadithi, the hero!</i>

04:52.463 --> 04:54.560
<i>♪ Oh, I must agree</i>

04:54.565 --> 04:56.528
<i>♪ Hadithi, the hero!</i>

04:56.533 --> 04:59.044
<i>♪ It's all about me!</i>

04:59.049 --> 05:00.528
<i>♪ Ravens I have rescued</i>

05:00.533 --> 05:03.027
<i>♪ Freed finches from the fray</i>
(YELPS)

05:03.032 --> 05:04.336
<i>♪ And the Egret's great escape</i>

05:04.341 --> 05:07.039
<i>♪ Oh, that was a busy day</i>

05:07.044 --> 05:10.476
<i>♪ But most of all I'm famous
for that legendary wing</i>

05:10.481 --> 05:13.178
<i>♪ Against 10 hungry crocodiles</i>

05:13.183 --> 05:16.382
<i>♪ With my Hadithi spin</i>

05:16.387 --> 05:18.117
