05:32.369 --> 05:36.302
<i>♪ Yes, I must truly be humbled</i>

05:36.307 --> 05:40.372
<i>♪ By all my fanatical fans</i>

05:40.377 --> 05:44.310
<i>♪ Yes, it's so hard
to be humble</i>

05:44.315 --> 05:48.213
<i>♪ But that's just
the bird that I am</i>

05:48.218 --> 05:51.150
<i>♪ That I am</i>

05:51.155 --> 05:52.451
